			<div class="content" id="post-content-2466908">
									

<p>Psstt&#8230;it's totally <a href="/scp-527">SCP-527</a>. ;)</p>
<p>Also:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>Why was he only there once? (Why did the circus know he was only going to be there once?)</p>
</blockquote>
<p>No no, the circus is only there for one show every time they pop up. They need to keep appearances brief and spontaneous or the Foundation or the GOC would end up taking every last one of their freaks/performers. What's more interesting is <em>where the circus goes</em> when it packs up its stuff.</p>

